title: The Best of The Dan Patrick Show
itunes:title: The Best of The Dan Patrick Show
description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, DP reacts to James Harden's extension with the Sixers. Do they have what it takes to be a top team in the East? Jimmy G has been given permission to seek a trade out of San Francisco. Where will he end up? Plus,  Tiger's caddie Joe LaCava details what it was like walking up the 18th hole at St. Andrews.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
